The paper deals with algorithmic problems related to directed graphs and their subgraphs, which are typical topics in the sub-categories of cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics). The paper also involves approximation algorithms and complexity theory, which are relevant to cs.CG (Computational Geometry), cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory), and cs.CC (Computational Complexity).
